trailingComments.value:
*
 * @desc Defines a spherical shape for one or more {@link Mesh}es.
 *
 * ## Usage
 * Creating a {@link Mesh} with a SphereGeometry and a {@link PhongMaterial} with diffuse {@link Texture}:
 *
 * ````javascript
 * new Mesh(myViewer.scene, {
 *     geometry: new SphereGeometry(myViewer.scene, {
 *          center: [0,0,0],
 *          radius: 1.5,
 *          heightSegments: 60,
 *          widthSegments: 60
 *      }),
 *      material: new PhongMaterial(myViewer.scene, {
 *          diffuseMap: new Texture(myViewer.scene, {
 *              src: "textures/diffuse/uvGrid2.jpg"
 *          })
 *      })
 *  });
 ````

extra.rawValue: negative radius not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative radius not allowed - will invert

extra.rawValue: negative heightSegments not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative heightSegments not allowed - will invert

extra.rawValue: negative widthSegments not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative widthSegments not allowed - will invert

extra.rawValue: negative radius not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative radius not allowed - will invert

extra.rawValue: negative heightSegments not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative heightSegments not allowed - will invert

extra.rawValue: negative widthSegments not allowed - will invert

arguments.value: negative widthSegments not allowed - will invert
